{"tid":336244,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"D廢老學識買股票 真係害人不淺","createTime":"2017-07-26T09:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T12:36:27.000Z","uid":53209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d21d4f5ad440fbe1cb36d9855bada2ddbf9790c","tid":336244,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:32:12.000Z","msg":"大約7-8年前 我老母學識左樣野叫買股票 個陣我大約中三<br />\n然後佢仲戇鳩鳩到每個月比錢人叫人教佢買股票  大約一萬一個月<br />\n咁都算數啦 一萬一個月又唔係多<br />\n我個陣同佢講 你搵人返黎點NUMBER你買 你輸撚硬錢<br />\n佢又回我:人地專業架<br />\n我:專你老母咩 係勁洗撚幫你買?<br />\n佢:人地無錢買<br />\n我: 勁既點會無錢呀?<br />\n佢:你識乜呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁到佢買買下啦 可能嬴左一萬幾千 走去學人ALL IN<br />\n你話ALL IN HSBC依D 由150蚊趺撚到33蚊 我都可以話係個時代要你輸錢<br />\n但我老母 居然 走去ALL IN一隻仙股<br />\n佢同D朋友/親友傾計個陣比我聽到左 我即刻走去問佢 做乜鳩ALL IN 隻仙股? 傻撚左呀? 然後佢答我:日本紙黎姐<br />\n咁我當時中學生唔撚識野 以為佢買D咩日本股 用日元計數 咁日元好少姐就無再追問佢<br />\n<br />\n結果當然唔係日元係港元啦<br />\n <br />\n結果隻股票就幾乎買咁耐趺足咁耐 直到今日都仲未放<br />\n當中隻股票曾經係依7/8年內升返過唔少<br />\n到隻股票要供股 我同我老母講 供完隻股票跌硬 我老母唔撚信<br />\n結果唔夠一頭半個月 趺左一半<br />\n現價大約跌左8成左右 <br />\n合計蝕約3百萬 擺返去7/8年前 個到足足蝕撚左成層樓有多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩我打左個電話比我老母 求鳩佢放 佢終於應承我 希望佢真係會放<br />\n<br />\n 求安慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c44060aab381fcc4ac455724655bef132fd22e","tid":336244,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:36:30.000Z","msg":"希望佢真係會放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed230a84c42b9747ef7d6aa73bb39f4c0f1e7f4c","tid":336244,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:38:00.000Z","msg":"我老母對接左副身家啦"},{"pid":"d557d993ad0781bb721c5e75fe9487c5ee7ef64a","tid":336244,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:39:48.000Z","msg":"巴打睇得咁開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61869b520924f60e63438ee39564759e977eeb0","tid":336244,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:43:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51c80c27dc8044a11c31cd2b1b3e6f7af587d582","tid":336244,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:44:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f62301929dfbc8600a6010c9c27106d2088bab3","tid":336244,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:45:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打睇得咁開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我依加咪開POST上黎 講返依件事 減輕下心理壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3cc32ad52e218f0aec16fd00a4d4b74751052a","tid":336244,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:46:54.000Z","msg":"都趺左8成啦<br />\n放同唔放有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b13ed54425c997deb8fda7628aba3f29aa22756","tid":336244,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:49:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都趺左8成啦<br />\n放同唔放有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有幾十萬拎返"},{"pid":"31554c5a9c679af8eb18bbc074e807249c915c1a","tid":336244,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:53:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d79d5edaf68e4f2fdf9c2613e08faff7d9807f7b","tid":336244,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:57:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁又唔關廢老事<br />\n<br />\n好多後生都覺得自己係股神<br />\n<br />\n其實大家都係賭緊運</blockquote><br />\n個問題係 當我知道左件事之後 我一次又一次咁提醒佢 叫佢唔好聽人講NUMBER買 升返又叫佢放<br />\n<br />\n佢一唔係呃我 一唔係股神上身  信街外人都唔撚信自己個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果我老母無輸依筆錢 我諗我既人生可以有少少改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7915e368e54131e15220b84816b7b5d125e63683","tid":336244,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:58:39.000Z","msg":"叫佢轉同你買<br />\n你照價賠比佢"},{"pid":"f803dba6fa2b21349eb27a5b303330ad5c74b4cb","tid":336244,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁又唔關廢老事<br />\n<br />\n好多後生都覺得自己係股神<br />\n<br />\n其實大家都係賭緊運</blockquote><br />\n個問題係 當我知道左件事之後 我一次又一次咁提醒佢 叫佢唔好聽人講NUMBER買 升返又叫佢放<br />\n<br />\n佢一唔係呃我 一唔係股神上身  信街外人都唔撚信自己個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果我老母無輸依筆錢 我諗我既人生可以有少少改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢硬頸好勝都冇計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0ff7d9a4de989b097fd38593cf83f0b0a61eec","tid":336244,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:02:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都趺左8成啦<br />\n放同唔放有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有幾十萬拎返</blockquote><br />\n咁拎返仲有機賺返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d0d8b4cbd6cc922181b40937895170ff6e6c58","tid":336244,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>都趺左8成啦<br />\n放同唔放有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有幾十萬拎返</blockquote><br />\n咁拎返仲有機賺返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一隻無實業 以往升返都係比人炒上之後1,2日即時暴跌返 仲要年年蝕錢既仙股 我睇唔到轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae02f1af38b8d2dc28fe1baf218fc70e8bb29c0","tid":336244,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:30:22.000Z","msg":"又諗起一樣野 我老母個陣 仲攞埋我d利是錢去all in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有19定20萬 雖然錢都係佢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7e26fd4aeca97f73d5cf13a70c532e5b79cf4f","tid":336244,"uid":99209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:30:55.000Z","msg":"number 降"},{"pid":"e363cc2a6fe901eccc7f06ac01eb9faad22626dd","tid":336244,"uid":48277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:33:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你老母冇錯!<br />\n錯既係市場</span></span>"},{"pid":"356bf6e35c53bcb44f7bd41a72d6d06c57e834b9","tid":336244,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:33:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又諗起一樣野 我老母個陣 仲攞埋我d利是錢去all in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有19定20萬 雖然錢都係佢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個陣仲同我講 個20萬 叫我問我老豆攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(已經去左仙游)"},{"pid":"8ecaa4f6642b8dbb580282f9205a5578b2af578f","tid":336244,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:36:29.000Z","msg":"一萬一個月學投資都唔算多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ed7c33449be28fb582fe1417cca77a6e949b5f","tid":336244,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一萬一個月學投資都唔算多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我老母除左買股票之外 揾錢能力幾好<br />\n<br />\n我自問我作為一個大學生(佢無讀書)<br />\n應該一生都無機會揾得多錢過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e15a91238b1464e379f20e3c29714c6d27239c","tid":336244,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:46:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一萬一個月學投資都唔算多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我老母除左買股票之外 揾錢能力幾好<br />\n<br />\n我自問我作為一個大學生(佢無讀書)<br />\n應該一生都無機會揾得多錢過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有唔有錢同多唔多根本冇關<br />\n<br />\n教得好既話就一萬都唔多<br />\n教得唔好既話免費都唔洗佢教<br />\n<br />\n正如一個有錢人都唔會用$100食一個m記餐"},{"pid":"d0d7c2dff586aa42065fd76492a3a74b54396647","tid":336244,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T12:36:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一萬一個月學投資都唔算多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我老母除左買股票之外 揾錢能力幾好<br />\n<br />\n我自問我作為一個大學生(佢無讀書)<br />\n應該一生都無機會揾得多錢過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有唔有錢同多唔多根本冇關<br />\n<br />\n教得好既話就一萬都唔多<br />\n教得唔好既話免費都唔洗佢教<br />\n<br />\n正如一個有錢人都唔會用$100食一個m記餐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你啱 相對地係貴既<br />\n但就個金額而言 對我老母黎講又的確係唔算多"}]}